Body: IT AND DIGITAL TECHNOLOGIES The project provides the integration of the most actual elements of IT and digital technologies into the company's business model and includes three main modules:   BLOCKCHAIN-TECHNOLOGIES The Blockchain Technology module is responsible for a distributed registry that ensures the automation of all processes, reliability, and the 100% secure of project data storage, including the database of investors, the number of their tokens, the calculation and payment of profit. Body: CRYPTO-ASSETS: TOKENS AND CRYPTOCURRENCY The Crypto-assets module provides the issue of project tokens within GENESIS's framework. Project tokens are a digital dematerialized asset that is assured by real assets owned by the platform. GES token is not a surrogate of shares and/or other securities and guarantees its holder all the rights provided by the terms of the purchase of tokens. This type of crypto-assets certifies the right of the owner to get a share of profit from the commercial usage of real estate and guarantees its owner the right to participate in the activities of platform under agreed conditions and rules. Investors will enter the project by purchasing a certain number of tokens. Investors can leave the project by selling the tokens. A token is an accounting investment unit. The profit of investor is calculated and distributed according to the number of tokens owned by him/her. Title: [ANN][ICO] GENESIS - Investment in Real Estate
Body: How is GENESIS platform differs from the other? The activity of real estate blockchain startups divides into three types: • transfer of the registries on the blockchain; • transfer of real estate document management on the blockchain; • tokenization of real estate. Tokenization allows transforming real estate objects into more liquid economic value, total volume of which reaches 200 trillion dollars. Even a small part of this amount can effect cryptoeconomy. Unlike the other plarforms working with real estate tokenization, GENESIS is not a intermediary. GENESIS is a real estate fund, all the objects belong to the platform and GES tokenholders. This is the main benefit of our project. By investing into GENESIS you buy a share in real estate that belongs to you – not anyone else.  https://d.radikal.ru/d33/1806/fe/2e29430f1b59.jpg

Author: myops
Title: [ANN][ICO] GENESIS - Investment in Real Estate
Body: How to calculate the profit from investment in rent?  Consider two options: 1. The pessimistic, when the value of GENESIS assets is 3 000 000 EUR and realization of projects DEVELOP-GEN is 500 000 EURO per year. In this case, we focus on the classic profitability, because for small objects the overhead costs are higher: 3 000 000 x 12,24% = 367 200 EUR-rental income 500 000 x of 33.75% = 168 750 EUR – income from special projects The total income of platform will be 535 950 EUR. This is about 15.5% per annum.  https://d.radikal.ru/d15/1806/1a/b4949ba2ef0e.jpg

Author: myops
Title: [ANN][ICO] GENESIS - Investment in Real Estate
Body: 2. The optimistic, when the value of Genesis assets is 30 000 000 EUR and the realization of projects DEVELOP-GEN is 8 000 000 EURO per year. Here we take the income of GENESIS, because the overhead costs are reduced: 30 000 000 x 13.46% = 4 038 000 EUR – rental income 8 000 000 x 33.75% = 2 700 000 EUR-income from special projects The total income of platform will be 6 738 000 EUR. That is about 18% per annum. Taking into account the additional services and services appearing on our platform, as well as the reduction of overhead costs, the real profit for investors will be 20-25% per year. At the same time, we do not take into account the growth of GES token and passive income due to the discounts on utility token NES.  https://d.radikal.ru/d08/1806/b7/13f5a0783099.jpg

Title: [ANN][ICO] GENESIS - Investment in Real Estate
Body: We are realizing the project of "51 the idea" on the basis of multifunctional platform. Each member of the community will be able to participate in the improving of our platform and become a member of team. Our main task is to expand the services provided by GENESIS platform and increase the ability to implement new ideas on the existing technical solution.  How the project of "51 ideas" works»  The coordinator of committee accepts the applications with proposals for the introduction of additional services on GENESIS platform. Together with the author of idea the coordinator prepares the presentation material for the members of commission. The commission meets once every 3 months. Based on the results of study of presented project, the decision about further actions is made. If the project passes the examination, the author of idea gets an opportunity to become the part of GENESIS team and introduce the project into platform. The record of transfer of applications is stored on blockchain.

Body: "The investment strategy of project provides the obligatory listing of GES tokens on cryptocurrency exchanges. The listing of tokens on cryptocurrency exchanges will be done upon reaching the planned levels of operational activity. The approximate date of listing of GES tokens on cryptocurrency exchanges is set on second half of 2019. The estimated financial models used for the forecasting of possible variation of exchange rate of GES tokens took into account the reaching of planned levels of operational activity of project, show that exchange rate of GES tokens within 6 to 9months after the listing can reach 3.0 – 7.5 euro for 1 GES with a nominal price 1 euro for 1 GES. The listing of GES tokens on cryptocurrency exchanges is possible before the second half of 2019 if the project will achieve the planned values of target indicators early."

Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] GENESIS - Investment in Real Estate
Body: Yes.  "THE ADVANTAGES OF GES TOKEN: GUARANTEED BY REAL ASSETS GES token is guaranteed by assets, related to the highest level of guarantee – by real estate. Volatility of cryptocurrency and possible collapses of cryptocurrency cannot negatively affect to the rate of GES tokens, as its price is determined and based on the value of real estate and the profitability of project. COMPANY’S OBLIGATION FOR REPURCHASE One of the key parameters for investors is the obligation of company to repurchase the tokens. The investor will be able to exercise the right to leave the project and sell the tokens back to the company at any time after starting the operational activity of project. PUBLIC OFFERING ON INTERNATIONAL EXCHANGES AND STRONG GROWTH RATE The investment strategy of project provides the obligatory expansion of GES tokens on international cryptocurrency exchanges. The financial forecast demonstrates that during 6-9 months after public offering on the exchanges, the rate of token can grow up to 300%-750%. GES TOKEN IS A PIECE OF REAL ESTATE All real estate owned by GENESIS platform will be tokenized, you will own your part of real estate, according to the amount of investments. THE OPPORTUNITY TO PARTICIPATE IN SPECIAL HIGH-YIELDING PROJECTS The holders of GES tokens will get profit from the realization of special projects. It will provide the additional income of 25%-75% to investors."

Title: [ANN][ICO] GENESIS - Investment in Real Estate
Body: The blockchain is increasingly used in the field of real estate Back in 2017, Georgia thought about the possible use of blockchain in real estate. In early 2018, Georgia announced the introduction of pilot project, which provides the creation of the land cadastre based on blockchain technology. The creators of project believe that the blockchain will replace the notary Institute. In their opinion, the blockchain includes three fundamental principles. The first, it is the security of data that can not be lost or damaged (for example, unlike the paper documents). The second, the audit of the registry on blockchain can be carried out in real time, even every 15 minutes, if it is necessary. The third, the blockchain will reduce the cost of the registration process of property rights by excluding the intermediaries.

Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] GENESIS - Investment in Real Estate
Body: THE PROJECT'S RELIABILITY AND INVESTMENT ATTRACTIVENESS Real estate has historically been considered the best way to save wealth and one of the most reliable types of investment. However, some players still use risky schemes that include investing money in illiquid real estate, and various fraudulent schemes are not uncommon. Our project do not to take part in risky deals, which is guaranteed by a pre-sale audit of each property by specialized companies, as well as a risk-free, confident investment strategy. At the early stage of GENESIS (ITO), we are going to invest only in ready-to-use commercial and business properties. An obligatory condition is its high liquidity and a signed long-term contract with existing renters. The policy of GENESIS does not allow investing in high-risk assets, such as unfinished construction, long-term projects from unknown developers, and projects without state control over the construction.

Author: heavensuperman
Title: [ANN][ICO] GENESIS - Investment in Real Estate
Body: 1. France and Germany want to have a public debate about bitcoin (and possibly other cryptocurrencies). The topic of "cryptocurrency regulation" is one of the most important on the agenda of G-20 summit.  2. The operational model of project provides investors with the opportunity to choose the real estate for purchase. Investors will be given the right to choose among the objects of equal economic attractiveness. Voting procedure will be realized on the basis of blockchain technology. The opportunity to choose the real estate for all investors increases the economic attractiveness of GENESIS for a wide range of investors, not only institutional but also a private and creates the mechanisms for investors to control the development and operating of project.  3. After the legalization of the cryptocurrency in Belarus public attention to the cryptcurrency and the digital technologies has greatly increased. It should be added that according to the proposed law activities related to the use of tokens will receive tax benefits or will be free of tax.  4. Regular reporting to investors and regular internal audit are obligatory conditions for the proper operation of GENESIS. In addition, before including the real estate into the company's investment pools, every property is estimated by an independent organization. Our current choice for audit and rating is one of the largest European companies with a high trust rating. We believe that the above principles will ensure transparency in the company's operation, and, as a result, will increase the project's trust level.

Author: veranika55
Title: [ANN][ICO] GENESIS - Investment in Real Estate
Body: In real estate, blockchain can help to organize new forms of registries, titles of ownership and transactions. Blocks recorded in the blockchain system will certify the process of transfer of ownership of the property-money transfers, contracts and data of the owner will be confirmed.  This will help eliminate the middlemen who take a commission in the process of real estate transactions - lawyers, realtors, notaries and employees of registration chamber. Minimum is from 1-2% of the transaction amount. In addition, the risks of fraud (for example, when renting or selling apartments) and the time to prepare transactions and certificates will be reduced. Specialized blockchain platforms will prevent data forgery, simplify the processes of checking real estate before selling, customers will have access to platforms 24/7.  Read more here: http://www.forbes.ru/biznes/347775-nedvizhimost-i-blokcheyn-pochemu-tehnologiya-perevernet-rynok

Author: kapa6ac
Title: [ANN][ICO] GENESIS - Investment in Real Estate
Body: Every real estate transaction goes through the multiple listing service (MLS), which tracks what agents represent which clients, contracts, listing agreements, appraisals and more. However, the MLS is notoriously fragmented. The information is decentralized and restricted, making access difficult for people who are not real estate professionals. It’s often out-of-date as well, which hampers an agent’s ability to make comparisons and spot trends.

Author: veranika55
Title: [ANN][ICO] GENESIS - Investment in Real Estate
Body: REIT does not allow to work with cryptocurrency, tokens and blockchain. Only the best will be borrowed from the REIT!  Let me explain what is REIT  The REIT block means that the company's business model includes some operational and functional business processes of Real Estate Investment Trusts. The REIT block will ensure the transparency of the GENESIS's operation, mandatory reporting and auditing, voting mechanisms on the issues of project development, the procedure for the formation and allocation of the development fund, and the opportunity for investors to withdraw from the project following the company's obligations to redeem the tokens. The REIT block ensures reliability of the company, safeguards investors' interests, and accommodates engaging conservative and institutional investors.

Author: veranika55
Title: [ANN][ICO] GENESIS - Investment in Real Estate
Body: Genesis is not an intermediary platform, but an ICO, which will purchase commercial real estate objects for collected money, and then rent them out.  They are not a platform for connecting people together, they are a platform that owns real estate and receives income from its commercial use. All investors who have bought ICO tokens will receive profit from the rental of real estate, which will be credited to their account. Investors through the internal exchanger can exchange the profit for any cryptocurrency or Fiat money or buy tokens. Tokens of ICO Genesis will be secured by real estate, which bought the Genesis on the money raised from investors.
